\frametitle{Direct detection: New notation and model parameters}

Define the parameters:
\pause
\begin{align*}
\alert<3>{r_{\rho}} \equiv \frac{\rho_2}{\rho_1}\;,\quad \alert<3>{r_{\sigma}} \equiv \frac{\sigma_2^p}{\sigma_1^p} \;,\quad C(r_\rho,\sigma_1^p) \equiv \frac{\rho_{\rm loc}\,\sigma_1^p}{2 \,(1+r_\rho)\,m_p^2} \,.
